// Hall of Bosses — a grand pantheon connecting the three boss arenas.
//
// This is the in-world boss hub: accessible from central_hub_main via a
// door at x=1357, y=880.  Three shrine zones — one per boss — open onto
// portals to the individual arenas.
//
// Layout (1200 wide × 512 tall):
//
//   +--------------------------------------------------------------------+  y = 0
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒  |
//   |  Clockwork Warden shrine  ▒pillar▒  Mockingbird shrine  ▒pillar▒  |
//   |                                                       GNU-ton shrine|
//   |     ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░              ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░       ░░░░░░░░░░░  |  ← perches
//   |                                                                      |
//   | [hub door] [warden portal]    [mockingbird portal]  [gnu-ton portal]|
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒  |  y = 480
//   +--------------------------------------------------------------------+
//
// Clockwork Warden and Mockingbird portals are one-way outbound: the
// player enters the arena via the hall and returns via that arena's own
// exit door (back to the basement hub or pirate cove respectively).
// The GNU-ton portal is bidirectional: gnu_ton_arena's exit returns
// the player to the hall.

